      "message": "I do not support this.  I would prefer to see a stack-then-heap allocator that slots into std::vector/set, or SkTArray.h refactored to build in skslc\u0027s standalone configuration, or skslc\u0027s standalone configuration to be somehow made moot.  We\u0027re piling up idiosyncrasies to support each other here.",
